>
>The Hamamatsu P3062-01 IR photoreflector mentioned in MR was discontinued
and
>replaced by the P5587.  This chip has the identical pinout and dimensions
as
>the original.  I
>ordered several from Hamamatsu last year but they are pricey (~$7/ea) in
small
>quantities.
>They are very thin (~1.7mm) and have a focal distance of about 3 mm.
>You can check to see if they are still available at 908-231-0960.
